FBIS3-57695 "drsov019_t_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-019 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Jan 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Finance Minister Named Representative to EBRD WS2701175994 Tallinn ETA NEWS RELEASE in English 1411 GMT 27 Jan 94 WS2701175994 Tallinn ETA NEWS RELEASE Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] Estonia's Government appointed new Finance Minister Heiki Kranich the country's representative at the boards of governors of the European Bank for Development and Reconstruction (EBRD) and the World Bank. [passage omitted] Kranich was also appointed Estonian coordinator at economic cooperation programmes with the Commission of the European Communities and G-24.
